# Worker metrics — submit CPU + temp every minute.
# Install with `crontab -e` (or copy this file and edit the path):
#   * * * * * /home/admin/cluster-manager/agents/worker-health/metrics.py >> /home/admin/cluster-manager/agents/worker-health/metrics.log 2>&1
#
# psutil's cpu_percent(interval=1) blocks for 1 second, so the script takes
# ~1.5s wall time. Cron's 1-minute granularity is plenty.
* * * * * /home/admin/cluster-manager/agents/worker-health/metrics.py >> /home/admin/cluster-manager/agents/worker-health/metrics.log 2>&1
